data.description: Interface for DataFax system from CDSI
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
DataFax system is a fax-based data collection system developed by
    Clinical DataFax system Inc (http://www.datafax.com/). The module is
    the base module for extracting, transfering and loading the
    databases in DataFax system into a relational database. It is also
    the parent module for web-enabling the DataFax reports.
